    v1 = 0.15
    v1 = ((0.23 + (tmp + 0.89 * tmp + 0.41)) * v2)
    v2 = (wp.sin((v2 + 0.80 - v0 + 0.30)) + (0.43 * v1))
    v2 = 0.16
    tmp = (wp.abs(v2) + v0)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(wp.sin(v0 + 0.94)))
